OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778778357
OL,3,CBrave rape victim's testimony convicts
OL,4,Cattacker in city centre
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for the rape and
OL,7,Ffalse imprisonment of an "extremely
OL,8,Fvulnerable" woman.
OL,10,FBenjamin Wilson, 33, was sentenced to
OL,11,F10 and a half years in prison after
OL,12,Ftargeting his victim who had become
OL,13,Fseparated from friends during a night
OL,14,Fout in Manchester in June 2022.
OL,16,FThe woman, who suspected her drink had
OL,17,Fbeen spiked, was repeatedly assaulted
OL,18,Fby Wilson, a stranger she encountered
OL,19,Fnear a city centre takeaway.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
