PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778778357
OL,3,CBrave rape victim's testimony convicts
OL,4,Cattacker in city centre
OL,6,FWilson took advantage of the victim's
OL,7,Fintoxicated state, guiding her into a
OL,8,Ftaxi and taking her to a flat before
OL,9,Frepeatedly raping her.
OL,11,FThe following morning, he dropped her
OL,12,Fnear her hotel where she was due to
OL,13,Fstay with friends. She reported the
OL,14,Fincident soon afterwards.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,17,Fthe victim's testimony, in particular,
OL,18,Fhelped detectives build their case,
OL,19,Fleading to Wilson's arrest at his home
OL,20,Fin Derbyshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
