PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778778357
OL,3,CBrave rape victim's testimony convicts
OL,4,Cattacker in city centre
OL,6,FDC Phillip Sargeant said: "I am
OL,7,Fawestruck not only by the courage of
OL,8,Fthe victim in coming forward, but also
OL,9,Fby her patience and resilience in
OL,10,Fwaiting for justice.
OL,12,F"The impact on her, her family and her
OL,13,Fsupport network has been profound. I
OL,14,Fhope today's sentence provides some
OL,15,Fmeasure of closure and enables them to
OL,16,Fmove on from this traumatic experience.
OL,26,@nD@[OU
