OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778778357
OL,3,CBrave rape victim's testimony convicts
OL,4,Cattacker in city centre
OL,6,F"We have worked hard to support her
OL,7,Fthroughout, allowing her to guide the
OL,8,Fpace of the investigation and how she
OL,9,Fengaged with the process. I hope this
OL,10,Fcase reassures others that they will
OL,11,Fbe taken seriously and supported
OL,12,Fsensitively by Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice, no matter how long it takes."
OL,15,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,16,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,17,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,18,Four region.
